  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Ofqual's Chief Regulator responds to The Secretary of State for Education about the package of measures for GCSE, AS and A level qualifications in 2021. </p>

  </div>
</div>

